488
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ulazimo u odnos?

489
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] S kakvim partnerom ulazimo u odnos?

490
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:54,000
